import React from'react'

import { BrowserRouter,route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from  './Home.js'

import About from './About.js'

import Services from './Services.js'

import Contact from './Contact.js'

function App()
 { 
return(
<>
<browserRoute>

<route/>
        <Home />
        <About />
        <Services />
        <Contact/>


</browserRoute>
        </> )
             }

export default App
